<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id1222e476-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777" identifier="/us/usc/t44/s904"><num value="904">§ 904.</num><heading> Congressional Record: maps; diagrams; illustrations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Maps, diagrams, or illustrations may not be inserted in the Record without the approval of the Joint Committee on Printing.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id1222e477-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/620">Pub. L. 90–620</ref>, <date date="1968-10-22">Oct. 22, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1256">82 Stat. 1256</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
